He believs in healthy life.

326
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:13,020
Early to bad, early to wake up.

327
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:16,351
I'll do like him,
I'm going to sleep.

328
00:38:17,140 --> 00:38:19,746
And I do not want you to be disturbed till
tomorrow morning. Understand?

329
00:38:20,700 --> 00:38:22,111
Otherwise, I can loose my temper.

330
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:34,147
- I could't do anything, Mantas?
- Enough.

331
00:38:35,220 --> 00:38:36,984
You stinky yellow coyote.

332
00:38:38,020 --> 00:38:40,705
Nobody tells that to Mantas.

333
00:38:41,020 --> 00:38:42,829
You upset me when I'm trying to eat...

334
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:45,870
But this damn Sartana.
I cursed his mother.

335
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:49,191
All right, all right. Do not be nervous.

336
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:51,024
Too much money is involved.

337
00:38:57,140 --> 00:38:59,586
You make a mistake, if you think your
little money could do everything.

338
00:38:59,740 --> 00:39:01,424
Everyone gets the money.

339
00:39:01,580 --> 00:39:04,629
But you must first
get rid of Sartana.

340
