It will not be difficult.

341
00:39:08,700 --> 00:39:09,826
Fine.

342
00:39:10,260 --> 00:39:14,470
You must do this before Spencer
sends next shipment.

343
00:39:15,260 --> 00:39:18,150
And remember that Sartana
is far from bing stupid.

344
00:39:18,300 --> 00:39:19,108
You must be careful, Mantas.

345
00:39:19,340 --> 00:39:21,502
He's dangerous and very fast.

346
00:39:21,820 --> 00:39:23,584
