He thinks, he's smart...

350
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:42,505
...but Mantas is smarter.

351
00:39:43,060 --> 00:39:44,949
We know the way he shoots.

352
00:39:46,220 --> 00:39:47,460
Of course.

353
00:39:48,420 --> 00:39:51,424
I send Caetano and two men
to do the job.

354
00:39:52,220 --> 00:39:53,221
Caetano is young,

355
00:39:53,740 --> 00:39:55,151
ambitious and very fast.

356
00:39:55,620 --> 00:39:58,305
