I'll get the horse.

360
00:41:12,980 --> 00:41:15,221
He asked not to be disturbed.

361
00:41:16,160 --> 00:41:18,742
Do not worry about it. From now on
it will rest in peace, Angelo.

362
00:41:19,260 --> 00:41:20,500
Be sure of that.

363
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:22,750
And better if you stay calm...

364
00:41:23,020 --> 00:41:24,829
...and do not open your mouth.

365
00:41:25,380 --> 00:41:28,987
Otherwise, we'll transform you
into an angel with small wings.

366
00:41:30,740 --> 00:41:31,821
Come on.

367
