Naked as a baby.

368
00:42:22,940 --> 00:42:23,987
Hello, my friends!

369
00:42:26,140 --> 00:42:27,710
"Farewell" is more appropriate.

370
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:31,909
The bathtub will be your coffin.

371
00:42:34,380 --> 00:42:36,269
I am completely clean,
I don't want to get spotted with blood.

372
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:37,865
Do not worry.

373
00:42:38,300 --> 00:42:39,461
We always carefully
carry out the work.

374
00:42:39,700 --> 00:42:42,385
