A moment.

377
00:42:50,900 --> 00:42:52,629
I want beautiful funeral.

378
00:42:53,220 --> 00:42:55,302
Do you understand? Promise me.

379
00:42:55,820 --> 00:42:57,424
Of course, I'll pay you.

380
