405
00:44:42,780 --> 00:44:45,863
And then what? Baxter is always there.

406
00:44:46,580 --> 00:44:48,662
The gold will be replaced with sand instead.

407
00:44:48,820 --> 00:44:49,867
Please!

408
00:44:50,660 --> 00:44:51,821
Paco! Cook this ...

409
00:44:56,220 --> 00:44:58,143
Bring him a boiled egg.

410
00:44:59,100 --> 00:45:00,306
Yes.

411
00:45:00,660 --> 00:45:02,742
Yes, and make sure it's fresher than this.

412
00:45:06,100 --> 00:45:09,229
Mescal, if you continue, I'll kill you.
