437
00:47:51,300 --> 00:47:52,461
Who is this?

438
00:47:53,340 --> 00:47:54,501
You know him?

439
00:47:54,660 --> 00:47:55,866
I've never seen before.

440
00:48:11,820 --> 00:48:13,345
Look who came.

441
00:48:25,260 --> 00:48:27,308
This gin tastes bad.

442
00:48:27,460 --> 00:48:30,748
This is normal.
Everything is rotten here.

443
00:48:30,900 --> 00:48:32,311
Isn't it??

444
00:48:34,820 --> 00:48:36,231
But I guess...

