499
00:52:55,820 --> 00:52:56,821
Obviously.

500
00:52:56,980 --> 00:52:58,948
All players like to win...

501
00:53:00,060 --> 00:53:01,550
...but only few succeed.

502
00:53:07,060 --> 00:53:09,427
- Can I join you?
- Why not?

503
00:53:10,140 --> 00:53:11,869
I have nothing against it.

504
00:53:12,020 --> 00:53:14,387
It will be very entertaining.

505
00:53:14,540 --> 00:53:16,383
